CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: XWELL Inc is a health and wellness holding company. It is an airport retailer of spa services through XpresSpa locations, offering travelers premium spa services, including massage, nail, and skincare, as well as spa and travel products. It operates four brands: XpresCheck, XpresSpa, Treat, and HyperPointe. XpresSpa is an airport retailer of wellness services and related products. Treat is a travel health and wellness brand that offers in-airport spa and wellness medical services. XpresCheck provides Covid-19 screening and diagnostic testing in partnership with the CDC. HyperPointe is a digital healthcare and data analytics relationship company.
